        <section class="caaft-ar-what-we-offer py-90"><div class="container"><header class="caaft-ar-offer-header"><h2 class="caaft-ar-offer-h2">Common Challenges Receivable &amp; Payable Management Solves</h2><p class="caaft-ar-offer-intro">Most businesses seek professional AR and AP support when facing one or more of these:</p><p class="caaft-ar-offer-intro">Invoices issued but not consistently tracked — leading to delayed or missed collections</p><p class="caaft-ar-offer-intro">Vendor payments missed or duplicated due to disorganised payable records</p><p class="caaft-ar-offer-intro">No visibility into aging receivables or which balances are critically overdue</p><p class="caaft-ar-offer-intro">Cash flow shortfalls caused by poor alignment between incoming and outgoing payments</p><p class="caaft-ar-offer-intro">Financial disputes with customers or vendors arising from incomplete documentation</p><p class="caaft-ar-offer-intro">Management making decisions without accurate, current working capital data</p><p class="caaft-ar-offer-intro">CAAFT's structured approach addresses each of these — moving businesses from reactive payment chasing to proactive, organised financial management.</p></header></div></section>
